title: I did something in settings and now it always talks to me, but won't let me in to change anything
content: I really don't know what to do.  It will not allow me to do anything.  It tells me often to tap twice to confirm or something, but I do not know where it means to tap.  I have tried everywhere I know.  Every time I push the time or whatever, it says time or whatever it is.  I can get to main screen, but I cannot go to settings or really anything else.
category: Google Assistant and Voice Actions, Google Pixel 4a (5G)
